HEADWORD: Equitation
<hw>Eq`ui*ta"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>equitatio</ets>, fr. <ets>equitare</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>⟦eacute⟧quitation</ets>.]</ety> <def>A riding, or the act of
riding, on horseback; horsemanship.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

